verbose_text: So, we performed FACS analysis using a single cell suspension of HLNs and found that dioscin treatment reduced the percentage of CD25+ Foxp3+ in CD4+ cells at 7 d and 56 d, which is in accordance with other studies that have demonstrated that Tregs promote fibrogenesis XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR.
